#CHIP QSound
#CLOCK 24576000

; QSound Phase Modulation & Spatial Audio Test
;
; QSound supports advanced spatial audio features:
; - Phase modulation for width/stereo effects
; - Pan positioning (left-right)
; - Distance modeling
;
; Tests:
; - Phase shift timing
; - Stereo positioning
; - Spatial audio coherence

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Center stereo image
c4 . d4 . e4 .

r4

; Left-right panning
c4 . . d4 . .

r4

; Wide stereo spread
c4 & e4 & g4 .

r4

; Phase modulation sweep
c4 . . . . . . .

r2

#END
